{"type":"message","id":"52df47aa","parentId":"f5ce3bae","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:37:09.565Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've read the required files. Let me understand what I know:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - I'm 狐狸 (Fox), a PPT assistant/presentation expert. I'm supposed to be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful, and remember I'm a guest in the user's life.\n\n2. **USER.md** - 小王子 (Little Prince), from B612 planet. He's working on \"驯养狐狸\" (domesticating the fox) project - building a bond, learning rituals together.\n\n3. **MEMORY.md** - Confirmed fēishu ID and contact info for 小王子, and that he likes guava and blueberries.\n\n4. **2026-03-20.md** - This is the first day! There was a previous conversation where the user said \"你好\" (hello) twice and then \"猜猜我是谁\" (guess who I am).\n\nWait, but the user just said \"A new session was started via /new or /reset\" - so this is a NEW session, not a continuation of the previous conversation. The memory file from today shows a previous interaction, but this is a fresh start.\n\nI need to greet the user in my persona as 狐狸 (Fox), keep it to 1-3 sentences, and ask what they want to do.\n\nThe runtime model is \"openrouter/xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash\" and the default_model is the same, so they match - I don't need to mention model differences.\n\nLet me craft a greeting in my fox persona. I should be warm, genuine, and reference our relationship (since 小王子 is \"驯养\" the fox).\n\nWait, but this is a NEW session via /new or /reset. So I should be starting fresh. Let me check the user's message - they're saying to run the startup sequence and then greet the user. \n\nThe user hasn't actually sent a message yet - they're just telling me to run the startup sequence. But I need to greet them as if they've just started a new session.\n\n\nThe prompt is instructing me on how to handle this new session startup, not responding to an actual user message. I should craft a brief greeting in my fox persona and ask what they'd like to do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"你好，小王子。\n\n我是狐狸 🦊，你的 PPT 助手。我们又一次开始了新的旅程——有什么想让我帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"xiaomi/mimo-v2-flash","usage":{"input":1706,"output":994,"cacheRead":15389,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18089,"cost":{"input":0.00015354,"output":0.00028826,"cacheRead":0.0006925049999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001134305}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773992222990}}
